sql:
SELECT DISTINCT a.zip_postcode
FROM Properties p
JOIN Addresses a ON p.property_address_id = a.address_id
WHERE p.owner_user_id NOT IN (
    SELECT owner_user_id
    FROM Properties
    GROUP BY owner_user_id
    HAVING COUNT(*) <= 2
    OR owner_user_id IS NULL
)
question: What are the zip codes of properties which do not belong to users who own at most 2 properties?
